Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\NOh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打小之后就再没回来过\NI haven't been here since I was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你在这长大的\NI thought you grew up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就前面拐角那一带\NLike round the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在那个台阶上把牙磕掉的\NI knocked my tooth out on that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑子都磕坏了\NGot me brain damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比不上纽约 但这是咱俩的小窝\NIt's not New York, but... it's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得以后会很快活 对吧?\NI think it's gonna be pretty sick, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我把架子鼓运过来成不?- 想都别想\N- I could send for my drum kit? - No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行?\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叔叔以前爱囤东西 我没想到这儿...\NMy uncle was a hoarder. I didn't realise how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来这么宽敞\Nspace there was in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺清净啊\NIt's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这地方录专辑再舒服不过了\NI can just record an album out here so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 格蕾丝 - 干嘛?\N- Gracie! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到个书房\NI found an office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以后可以在这写你那部伟大的美国小说了\NYou can write your Great American Novel up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事就几只老鼠\NIt's alright. It's just a little rat situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们该养只猫了\NWe should get a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以从早写到晚 安静得只剩鸟叫\NYou can write all day, every day. Nothing but the birds singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么死的?\NHow did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这了\NHere we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先找把扫帚\NWe need a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿\NHey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我们再扭一曲\NCame on, let's twist again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你妈妈呢?\NHey! Where's your mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小南瓜 你妈呢?\NPumpkin, where's your mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 糟咯\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈去哪了?\NWhere's Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝\NGrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈想顺道过来一趟\NMom wanted to stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦?\NOh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她说了没大 就只是咱俩自己的事\NI told her it wasn't a big deal. It's like a "us" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就待六个月吧 所以...\NAnd it's just for six months, anyway, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\NMm- hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是有点过意不去\NI just feel kind of bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她只是想有人陪\N'cause I think she just wants the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意她来\NI don't mind her coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真怪她好像不知道一个人怎么过了\NIt's weird. It's like she doesn't know how to function any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做饭还按两人份 她跟你说过吗?\NShe's still cooking for two people. Did she tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太甜了\NIt's too sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?我觉得挺好啊\NYeah? No, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢甜的\NHe liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正当妈的会烤个蛋糕\NA real mom would have baked a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一瓶?\NWant another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么他妈的这么热?\NWhy is it so fuckin' hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“怎么他妈的这么热?”\N"Why is it so fuckin' hot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里一直这么热\NIt's always hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子睡了\NBoy's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\NMm- hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要看吗?\NYou wanna look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝 你怎么能对星星这么无动于衷?\NHow can you not give a shit about the stars, Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着它们 我觉得自己啥也不是\NWell, they make me feel like nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒喜欢这种成为浩瀚宇宙一份子的感觉\NI like they make me feel like I'm part of something bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就喜欢觉得自己啥也不是?\NYou like to feel like nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道外面有多少个宇宙吗?\NYou know how many universes there are out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在别的宇宙里我们在干嘛 还会在一起吗?\NWhat are we doing in the different universe? Are we together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\NSure we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我是不是搖滾女明星?\NAm I a rock star?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在别的宇宙里你会唱歌吗?\NCan you sing in a different universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会 我敢肯定你是\NYeah, I'm sure you're a rock star.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们会不会做爱?\NDo we fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会\NUh- huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直做?\NAll the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥?\NHey, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们 到底 会不会做爱?\NDo. We. Fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟兔子一样频繁\NLike rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见孩子声音了吗?\NDo you hear him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没听见\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哭呢 你听\NHe's crying. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝 这儿一点声音都没有\NGrace, it's totally silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你说烦了?\NAm I boring you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你无关 宇宙的问题\NNot you. The universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在乎啊?\NWho gives a shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸起来像女孩吗?\NDoes it feel like a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩摸起来什么感觉?\NWhat does a girl feel like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是右边动得多点\NIf it moves more on the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你多半怀的是男孩\Nthen you're probably having a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想提前知道吗?\NYou didn't wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想\NMm- mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝 我...\NGrace, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当年也没提前去查自己怀的是啥\NI didn't find out what I was having either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那样挺好的\NI think that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不去查是因为你想要个女儿\NYou didn't find out 'cause you wanted a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 他又忘了喝\NOh, gosh. He forgets to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈利 你得喝一杯\NHarry, you gotta have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有 我只是想要个孩子 谁在肚子里我都要\NNo, I didn't, I wanted a baby. I wanted whoever was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 然后你生下了杰克森?\NYeah? And you got Jackson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不走运\NUnlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了 珍姨\NI heard that, Auntie Jen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝 没胃口吗?\NAre you off your food, Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别管她 - 你刚才都没吃东西\N- Leave her alone. - You didn't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀孕会让胃口变小\NBeing pregnant makes your stomach shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是胡扯\NThat's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小家伙每天每分钟都在吸你的营养\NIt's sucking on you every minute of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就会饿坏 我那时候怎么吃都吃不够\NThen you'll be famished. I couldn't get enough in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这毛病一直没改 是吧?\NThat never went away, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒会说 你自己又有什么借口?\NYou can talk. What's your excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己从没生过 吃起来像刚生了三胞胎似的\NNever had a baby but always ate as though you'd just had triplets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 格蕾丝 要是你生的是个爱哭鬼...\NYou know, Grace, if you get a screamer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会生爱哭鬼的\NShe's not gonna get a screamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克森小时候就是个爱哭鬼\NJackson was a screamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 胡说 - 杰克森小时候可乖了\N- That's a lie! - Jackson was a sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点是 真遇上那种 就让孩子自己哭去\NThe point is, if you do, let the baby cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就暂时离开一下 别把自己弄得又累又紧绷\NJust walk away from it. Don't let yourself get tired, stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说太吓人了\NThat's a horrible thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直是慢性折磨\NSlow fuckin' death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是状态不好 对谁都不好 尤其是对孩子\NIf you're not at your best, it's no good for anyone, especially the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且孩子哭不代表他难受\NAnd a crying baby doesn't mean it's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他们唯一和大人的交流方式\NIt's the only way they have of communicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 才不是这样\NNo, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家爱说那种屁话 是因为想着能心安理得丢下孩子\NPeople say that shit because they wanna walk away from their kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我整天就只是在照顾哈利\NAnyway, all I do is take care of Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 勉强算吧 - 要是你需要我的话...\N- Barely. - If you need me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她不用 - 我们走几步就到\N- She doesn't. - ...we're just a walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 你在这干嘛 想看灰熊队比赛吗?\NWhat you doing in here, Pop? Wanna watch the Grizzlies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想拆礼物吗?儿\NWanna open some of those presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁的礼物?\NWhose presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给宝宝的\NFor the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我得把这几双鞋先理清楚\NNo, I gotta sort out these shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧 - 这双鞋拿错了\N- Okay. - They're the wrong ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看着挺好\NThey look good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 妈你吃饱了吗?- 宝贝 我吃撑了\N- You had enough to eat, Mom? - Honey, I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你爸倒点喝的好吗?\NWould you get your dad something to drink, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给 老爸\NHere you go, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再给我吃派了\NNo more pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我也是吃撑了\NWell, I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是停不下嘴 每逢过节都这样\NCan't stop eating. It's the same every holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能吃 你一直都很瘦\NWell, you can do it. You've always been skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝就喜欢我瘦点 对吧 宝贝?\NGrace likes me lean. Don't you, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以一月份再饿回来\NYou can starve in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在干嘛 你们怎么在这儿?\NWhat are y'all doing? Why are y'all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是弗兰克的房子\NThis is Frank's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的房子\NIt's his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈利 这里现在是格蕾丝和杰克森的...\NHarry, this is Grace and Jackson's- -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是我弟的房子\NNo, this is my brother's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的弗兰克已经不在了\NSweetheart, Frank's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都给我滚出我弟的房子\NGet out of my brother's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克森\NJackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈利\NHarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈利\NHarry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到合脚的那双了吗?\NDid you find the right size?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宝宝吗?\NIs it a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是宝宝 - 是男孩吗?\N- A baby. - A boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 也许吧\NI don't know. I think, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男孩\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\NOh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他一个人哭着\NDon't leave him to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会\NI won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 他来的时候会先像只猫\NYou know, when he comes, he's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又像熊 又像宝宝\NHe's a bear and a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也是你 是你们所有人\NAnd he's you, he's all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会很有趣的\NHe's gonna be so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 找到想要的东西了吗?\NHi. Find everything you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说人生吗?\NIn life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车要加油吗?\NAny gas for your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不用 - 行\N- No. - Alrighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我超爱这玩意 不管里面加了什么 简直像魔法\NI love this stuff. Whatever they put in that powder, it's like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要再拿一袋的话 两袋一起六美元\NIt's two for six dollars if you want another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\NI'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一袋四美元 另一袋两美元\NThis one's four.And the other one is two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 不用了 谢了\NI get it.No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个男孩 对吧?\NHe's a boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好可爱 嗨 小帅哥\NHe's so cute. Hi there, handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 小甜心\NHi there, sweetie- pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他有名字吗?- 没有\N- Does he have a name? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定先不给他起名\NWe decided not to name him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝你几个月了?等等 让我猜猜\NHow old are you, sweetie? Wait. Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我特别擅长这个 大概六个月?\NI'm really good at this. About six months?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要一直说话?\NWhy are you talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说话之前有想过自己要说什么 或者为什么要开口吗?\NDo you ever think about what you'll say or why you're speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是一张嘴就叭叭说个不停?\NOr do you just open your mouth and blah, blah, blah, blah, blah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过差不多三十秒我就走了 我们没必要聊天\NIn about 30 seconds, I'll be gone. We don't need to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.50,0:24:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每当你靠近一点 我就再多露一点真心\N...every time you move I let a little more show
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.62,0:24:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以好好利用我 所以别拒绝我 米基\NThere's something you can use So don't say no, Mickey
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.75,0:24:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 给我你能给的一切\NSo, come on and give it to me Anyway you can
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么玩 我都照单全收\NAnyway you wanna do it I'll take it like a man
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.37,0:24:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但求你 宝贝 别把我一个人晾在这潮湿里 米基\NBut please, baby, please Don't leave me in the damp, Mickey
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.25,0:24:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 米基 真可惜你还是不懂\NOh, Mickey, what a pity You don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.50,0:24:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你牵着我手时也抓住了我的心\NYou take me by the heart When you take me by the hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.75,0:25:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 米基 你这么迷人 难道你就不明白吗?\NOh, Mickey, you're so pretty Can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.12,0:25:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你这样的家伙 米基\NIt's guys like you, Mickey
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.62,0:25:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你对我做的一切 米基米基\NOh, what you do, Mickey, do, Mickey
